               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra Māryām “Miracles of Mary” (fols. 1ra-4ra, 9ra-39vb, 58rb-62vb,
                     64ra-64vb)
 I-1) ʾƎsaggǝd laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki... “I worship Thee…” (fols.
                     1ra-4ra)
 II) Taʾammǝra Mikāʾel: (fols. 4ra-6vb)
 III) Zǝmmāre (fols.
                     6vb-8vb)
 I-2) Taʾammǝra Māryām: 33 miracles (fols. 9ra-39vb, 61ra-62vb,
                     64ra-64vb)
 IV) Dǝrsāna Mikāʾel, Homiliary for the feasts of St Michael
                     (fols. 40ra-51va)
 V) Taʾammǝra Qirqos: 2 miracles (fols. 54ra-58rb)
                     I-3) Introductory exhortation (fols. 58rb-61ra)
 VI) Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus: 1
                     miracle (fols. 63ra-64ra).</summary>
